{"type": "article", "id": 28220, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-15T06:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28984, "name": "Something"}, {"id": 17302, "name": "Layer"}, {"id": 28985, "name": "Narrative"}, {"id": 28986, "name": "Norton Point"}, {"id": 28987, "name": "Caroline Eriksson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151903mv40NDQbacqxIKhw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Collar collection by Something</h2>\n<p>如果你打算在家喝上一杯自己研磨的咖啡，意大利工作室 <a href=\"http://www.somethingdesign.com/\">Something</a> 最近为丹麦品牌 Stelton 设计的 Collar 是一套既满足了实用性又很美观的咖啡套装。Collar 包含了咖啡研磨机、糖碗、牛奶壶以及浓缩咖啡机，外观均为黑色的圆柱体，带给人一种朴素的质感。Collar 还有一些贴心的小细节，比如浓缩咖啡机采用木制把手，防止被烫伤。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163119W8oTFgHPesGYtZJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163121b2yAlIM5CktNsXV6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021631222Kiz5dNHwRnYq8Zh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163122OQXdVvGbSJYWjszM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80021368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163123wjnNiJgUIDkV4Gbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163123yo3fFAX0pDsCRGe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Charge Trays by Layer</h2>\n<p>曾推出过 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27425.html\">3D 打印轮椅</a>、<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27924.html\">弹性编织家具</a>的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/\">Layer</a> 最近与意大利陶瓷品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bitossiceramiche.it/bitossi/\">Bitossi Ceramiche</a> 合作推出了一套可充电托盘（<a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/projects/charge-trays/\">charge trays</a>）。通过手工家居以和无线充电技术的结合，托盘淡化了电子设备在家中产生的科技意味，可以更自然地和环境融为一体。托盘有四种大小以及釉面可供选择，底部的硅胶模块能够让工作室在未来出现更新的充电技术后对产品进行升级，让它成为一款不会过时的居家用品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216312458FXEroyJvp4neWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163125lNisuvQIgd6bVnYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163125lWszS3TAE1eiqVgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163126rkDtyW1FGVY74vOh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163126Tpq9ZgdbcRlF85U3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163127ksqtxHPDbpCGQEgc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Connesso by Caroline Eriksson</h2>\n<p>这个造型上并没有规则的白色扶手椅是设计毕业生 <a href=\"http://ikkionno.com/\">Caroline Eriksson</a> 的作品，曾在今年的米兰国际家具展上做过展出。Eriksson 在本应连接的地方采用了悬空的设计，同时保留了椅子的完整性，不对称的造型看上去相当大胆。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163127Twcv0gdeN8D4Ep1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163128ZDzWfSX6a1bn42do.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163128KeITXHS4baO9pMfF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021631281xovWCGEapJ9R3TL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Narrative Clip by Narrative</h2>\n<p>成立于 2012 年的 <a href=\"http://getnarrative.com/\">Narrative</a> 是一家致力于研发可穿戴相机的瑞典公司，Narrative Clip 就是公司旗下的产品，目前已经推出了第二代。这款相机的重量仅为 19 克，可以用别扣轻巧地扣在衣服上。镜头可以拍摄 800 万像素的照片或者 1080P 的录像，内置的 GPS 还可以记录下照片的拍摄地点，在默认设置下每 30 秒就会自动拍下照片。相机本身容量为 8GB，同时也会提供 10GB 的免费云储存空间。这款相机的售价为 199 美元，目前暂时售罄，你可以<a href=\"http://getnarrative.com/#pre-order\">通过链接</a>获取最新的销售情报。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163129X6SBejyD4qgwL8rx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65945166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163129EOCZ54Xx6aHrGdjs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73187184\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163130isWEcyuf1AawP02O.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163130y5KXNd2TEBFPY6oH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163131xgiINmPQjpa3GqJv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163132R4JvCKoE01MufhLB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Raw Fairies by Konrad Sybilski</h2>\n<p>伦敦排毒果汁品牌 Raw Fairies 最近委托 Konrad Sybilski 为旗下的生食和果汁设计了一套新的包装。通过透明的塑料瓶，果蔬的颜色一目了然，展现了绿色健康的理念。每一种果汁的风味以纤细的字体印刷在包装上并搭配了小巧精致的原料图片，下方还标注了果汁的营养价值。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163133XCvSayPJmKZpszxd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021631330YtuRW2misVETJNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163134uclC1XNG6WkheAVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68133333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163134XV3FctjwE654hbRL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163135BGwNq3D1TOgfQHyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216313589k5a6H41S2cCBEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Sea Plastic Differently by Norton Point</h2>\n<p>眼镜品牌 <a href=\"http://www.nortonpoint.com/\">Norton Point</a> 在前不久的世界海洋日推出了一款变废为宝的产品，用回收来的海洋塑料制作而成的 Sea Plastic Differently 太阳眼镜。这些塑料垃圾来自海地，由 Norton Point 的合作伙伴 The Plastic Bank 收集，随后进行处理加工，每一副眼镜都代表着约 453 克的海洋塑料以这种方式重生。如果你对这个项目感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nortonpoint/sea-plastic-differently-recycled-ocean-plastic-sun\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163136gPxldCiG83MVLHJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216313661BFrmbu8KxjwaCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37260677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163137mYezvjNU3fCrSXcV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163137DPFqo5yrJdbCwaXN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51911765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163138syjg7xDwMBrGeYWO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.59705882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}